{"tid":2178954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Biden搶閘係侵之前買咗\"Keep America Great\"嘅domain","createTime":"2020-08-28T18:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T18:57:37.000Z","uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a00e841740e7162f1430b0ca22d92eba274619","tid":2178954,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:39:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CBSNews/status/1299413861486022659?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBSNews%2Fstatus%2F1299413861486022659%3Fs%3D20&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=2fa1da0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBSNews%2Fstatus%2F1299413861486022659%3Fs%3D20&h=f276168f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CBSNews/status/1299413861486022659?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nThe &quot;Keep America Great&quot; website might sound like something that belongs to President Trump, but the site says it was paid for by Biden for President.<br />\n<br />\nMr. Trump's &quot;Make America Great Again&quot; slogan got a slight facelift for his 2020 presidential run, with the campaign adopting &quot;Keep America Great&quot; as its official new slogan.  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Keepamericagreat.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FKeepamericagreat.com&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=7a51ade8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Keepamericagreat.com</a>, however, features what it says are promises made by Mr. Trump that were broken. &quot;Trump isn't looking for a second term &ndash; he's looking for a do-over,&quot; the site says."},{"pid":"6b898fb7360867ac12518209b382ad4e64afcd59","tid":2178954,"uid":27210,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:40:52.000Z","msg":"On9 仔咁同侵助選有咩分別"},{"pid":"9da01aaf8f472aff7a6b89eaec6c63aa4c270822","tid":2178954,"uid":310700,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy"